Hello!

Welcome to the opening of Everlight!

This is the message box where we will be putting our announcements and updates/changelogs. Here you can keep up to date with the latest news, announcements, and community projects and events, as well as the changelog for each version!

Everlight is a Vanilla+ pack crafted to ensure that the game stays true to Vanilla while adding enough flavors to keep things interesting.
It's specifically designed for a good and simple multiplayer experience with your friends.

Explore a new kind of world generation that stays true to Minecraft with improved visuals(Only in Default & Quality) and a good selection of new blocks and furniture blocks to spice up your builds, as well as a bunch of quality of life features added to make your experience better.
Find structures in the wild as an Explorer, or build a cozy farm with a selection of new crops as a Farmer. Build yourself a store that provides services or items as a Shopkeeper, or enjoy participating in the events to come!

Play Everlight in the way you want!
Happy launch day! Now go punch some trees.

- Renpixel, Crim & Ash
